---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Garden & Outdoor Fulfillment | Heavy Items, Rust Prevention, Seasonal Peaks | MTP';
const description = 'Specialized fulfillment for garden equipment, outdoor furniture, camping gear. Heavy weight handling, rust/corrosion prevention &lt;70% humidity, 100% completeness verification, 48-hour delivery, 100% insurance.';
const ogImage = 'https://profm.ua/images/fulfillment-garden.jpg';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: title,
  description: description,
  provider: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'MTP Group',
    url: 'https://profm.ua/en/'
  },
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'Country',
    name: 'UA'
  },
  priceRange: '₴150-₴300'
};
---

<Base title={title} description={description} ogImage={ogImage} lang="en">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Garden &amp; Outdoor Fulfillment<br />Heavy Items, Rust Prevention, Seasonal Scaling
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95 leading-relaxed">
        Patio furniture, lawnmowers, grills, tents, fishing equipment. Heavy-duty handling, rust-prevention &lt;70% humidity, 100% completeness checks, seasonal peak flexibility, 48-hour delivery, 100% insurance.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Start Garden Fulfillment
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Garden &amp; Outdoor Needs Specialized Fulfillment</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">📦 Massive Weight &amp; Volume</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Lawnmower 50kg, grill 100kg, tent 15kg each. Requires heavy-duty pallet handling, specialized warehouse layout, and industrial forklifts. Standard logistics inadequate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💧 Rust &amp; Corrosion Risk</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Metal components rust at humidity &gt;70%. Wood warps and rots. Requires strict humidity control and protective packaging. One humid week causes permanent damage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🌞 Seasonal Demand Surges</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Spring/summer garden peaks: 1000+ orders in weeks. Requires flexible labor scaling, temporary storage, and rapid-turnaround delivery systems. Capacity must flex without waste.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔍 Complete Kit Verification</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Grill shipped missing grate, legs, cover = unsellable. Tent without poles, stakes, fabric = returned. Every piece must be verified before shipment or customer satisfaction fails.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

\1  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How MTP Group Handles Garden & Outdoor Orders</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          With 10 years of experience in specialized fulfillment and over 150 active clients, MTP Group has optimized every step of order processing. Our 3,900 m² warehouse is purpose-built for high-velocity fulfillment across diverse categories.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Fulfillment Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Garden product retailers sell bulky, heavy items—planters, tools, seeds, outdoor furniture. Orders often contain 5–12 items. Weight and volume create logistics challenges.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          MTP Group's approach: Garden items are organized by product type and weight. Heavy items are stored at waist height for ergonomic picking. Fragile items (ceramics, glass) are isolated. We use 5–20 ton vehicles for heavy deliveries. 4–6 minute picking time reflects the complexity of garden orders.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Retailers Choose MTP</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Garden margins are 30–40%. Delivery damage and delays hurt customer satisfaction. Our robust packing and on-time 24-hour delivery ensure zero-issue orders.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          MTP Group has processed <strong>10,000+ garden/outdoor orders processed, 18+ garden retailers served</strong>. Our experience in this category translates to faster integration, fewer picking errors, and predictable costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

   Garden &amp; Outdoor Services</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Heavy-Duty Specialized Packaging</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Lawnmowers in wooden crates with foam. Grills in reinforced cardboard with spacer bars. Tents in protective compression bags. Each item type gets custom protective packaging.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Rust Prevention: Humidity &lt;70%</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Dedicated warehouse climate control. Desiccant packets in metal item packaging. Protected shipping containers during rain/snow transit. Zero rust or corrosion on arrival.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ 100% Completeness Verification</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Before shipment: every part checklist verified. Grill has legs, grate, cover, tools. Tent has poles, stakes, guy-ropes, fabric. Control list saved with order documentation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Seasonal Peak Flexibility</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Spring surge? We scale labor 2-3x. Storage expands for seasonal inventory. Fast-tracked 48-hour delivery guaranteed even during peak season demand.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Pricing for Garden &amp; Outdoor</h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Picking, Verification, Delivery</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Picking per order</span>
            <span class="font-bold">50–100 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Specialized bulk packaging</span>
            <span class="font-bold">30–80 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% completeness verification</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Humidity control storage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">+100 UAH/pallet/mo</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>48-hour delivery (regional)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">150–300 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% insurance coverage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Example: Garden Store (60 orders/month seasonal)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Picking: 60 × 75 = 4,500 UAH<br/>
          Packaging: 60 × 55 = 3,300 UAH<br/>
          Delivery: 60 × 225 = 13,500 UAH<br/>
          Storage (3 pallets): 3 × 100 = 300 UAH/month<br/>
          <strong class="text-lg">TOTAL: 21,600 UAH/month = 360 UAH per order</strong><br/>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Includes: heavy-duty packaging, rust prevention, 100% completeness, seasonal scaling, 100% insurance</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Quality Guarantees</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">100%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Completeness Check</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Every piece verified before shipment</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">&lt;70%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Humidity Control</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Rust prevention for metal items</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">48h</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Guaranteed Delivery</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Even during seasonal peak demand</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Fulfillment Speed & Accuracy Matter for Your Business</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">⏱️ Speed = Competitive Advantage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">E-commerce customers expect 24-48 hour delivery. Slow fulfillment leads to lost orders and negative reviews. MTP Group's 2-4 hour order processing means your customers receive tracking updates the same day they order. This builds trust and encourages repeat purchases. Faster fulfillment also reduces storage costs by turning inventory quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">✅ Accuracy = Customer Retention</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Wrong item? The customer will return it, costing you both labor and shipping. Wrong quantity? Dispute and potential chargeback. Our 99.95%+ accuracy means customers receive exactly what they ordered—building satisfaction and driving 30-40% repeat order rates. Happy customers become your marketing channel through word-of-mouth and reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 Margins Are Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Fulfillment is often 10-20% of your total order cost. Partner with a provider who understands your margin structure and helps you optimize every step. MTP Group's transparent pricing and category expertise mean you pay only for what you use, with no hidden fees. Our 10 years of experience has helped 150+ retailers identify cost-saving opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔄 Scaling Without Stress</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Black Friday. Holiday season. New product launch. These peak periods either make or break your year. You need a fulfillment partner who scales with you—not one that delays orders during your busiest time. MTP Group guarantees 2-3x capacity scaling on 7 days' notice, ensuring your customers always get on-time delivery even during peak volume.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Secure Your Garden Fulfillment?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Heavy-duty packaging, rust prevention &lt;70% humidity, 100% completeness, seasonal scaling, 48-hour delivery, 100% insurance. Start today.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Request a Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}></script>
</Base>
